cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with generating realistic eye images that satisfy a given semantic segmentation mask while following the style of a specified person. This involves techniques related to computer vision (cs.CV) such as semantic segmentation and image synthesis, as well as graphics (cs.GR) for generating realistic images. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.MM) and principled approaches (cs.AI) for solving the problem. Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed methods (cs.LG).
